The paper discusses the technical challenges and solutions for using millimeter wave (mmWave) communications in future mobile networks, which involves topics related to information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), multimedia (cs.MM), communication (cs.COMM), and systems and control (cs.SY). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.IT, followed by cs.NI, cs.MM, cs.COMM, and cs.SY.
